    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素傷害</span>；<br>如果此技能為<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">重擊</span>，則使敵方出戰角色附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">引雷</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">引雷</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p>此狀態初始具有2層「引雷」；重複附屬時，疊加1層「引雷」。「引雷」最多可以疊加到4層。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>疊加1層「引雷」。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附屬角色受到蒼雷傷害時：</span>移除此狀態，每層「引雷」使此傷害+1。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/ead1e5139681f49400a80a2ebb10fb2a_2466692965499729276.png",
                "id": "talent33512",
                "key": "指尖雷暴",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "指尖雷暴"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>；如果敵方出戰角色未附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">引雷</span>，則使其附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">引雷。</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">引雷</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p>此狀態初始具有2層「引雷」；重複附屬時，疊加1層「引雷」。「引雷」最多可以疊加到4層。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>疊加1層「引雷」。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附屬角色受到蒼雷傷害時：</span>移除此狀態，每層「引雷」使此傷害+1。</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/af99fb6b223af8aab53e4447b06483ba_6530564617770320211.png",
                "id": "talent51280",
                "key": "蒼雷",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "蒼雷"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">薔薇雷光</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/e225f8fa5e9a435290d33b7b93b4e376_5019091539982815055.png",
                "id": "talent31015",
                "key": "薔薇的雷光",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "薔薇的雷光"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_3503104038388720780.png",
                "id": "talent15283",
                "key": "薔薇雷光",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/2b3f9718f47e31a775816000450f000e_2548078714259466370.png",
                "title": "薔薇雷光"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著雷元素，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點穿透傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點穿透傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下2次草元素或雷元素傷害+1的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[激化領域]</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_7877003626235034380.png",
                "id": "talent92027",
                "key": "雷元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重擊</span></strong></p><p>我方元素骰總數為偶數時進行的「普通攻擊」，視爲「重擊」。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗一層可用次數；</p><p>可用次數耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_322104926701321544.png",
